  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">When restructure earns its keep</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">If any of these sound familiar, the structure is fighting you.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:70ch;">Most owners reach for a chart of accounts redesign when reports stop answering the questions leadership asks.</p>
