  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">How a setup runs</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">From discovery to a chart you can build on.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:70ch;">Four phases, fixed fee, written scope.</p>
